### Await RxDB Synchronization In-Sync State (JavaScript)

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/replication.html

Waits until the RxDB replication is fully synchronized. This condition is met when the initial replication is complete, all local data has been replicated to the remote, and no replication cycles are currently running or in a retry state. Be cautious when using this with multi-instance replication, as it might not resolve until another instance closes its replication connection.

```javascript
await myRxReplicationState.awaitInSync();
```

